<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF666AD9FA5494FD1902B9F3" bold="true" box="[1448,1794,676,705]" pageId="157" pageNumber="918">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
<collectingRegion id="0650F81CFF666AD9F8F094FD1941B9F3" box="[1804,1857,676,705]" country="Cameroon" name="North" pageId="157" pageNumber="918">Not</collectingRegion>
assessed on The IUCN Red List. Virtually nothing is known about ecology of the Libo Tube-nosed Bat, and additional research is needed to clarity its conservation status.
</paragraph>
